{"id":31998,"date":"2019-06-13T11:11:01","date_gmt":"2019-06-13T07:11:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=31998"},"modified":"2024-08-22T14:22:37","modified_gmt":"2024-08-22T10:22:37","slug":"two-angels-come-with-sun","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/13\/two-angels-come-with-sun\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Angels: Two come every day and night"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>The sun never rises but that two angels are sent at its sides, calling out. All the earth&#8217;s inhabitants hear them, except humans and jinn: O people, come quickly to your Lord! What is little and sufficient is better than what is abundant and negligent! The sun never sets but two angels are sent at its sides, calling out. All the earth&#8217;s inhabitants hear them, except humans and jinn: O Allah, repay the one who spends in charity! O Allah, destroy the one who withholds charity!<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 21721<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064e\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0637\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0633\u064c \u0642\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u064f\u0639\u0650\u062b\u064e \u0628\u0650\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u062a\u064e\u06